{"tid":810631,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[I/A] Survival Heroes - 多人競技大逃殺生存遊戲 MOBA + Battle Royale","createTime":"2018-09-08T06:32:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-17T00:39:02.000Z","uid":66923,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"fa1108072363b7087349bdb196ba20c987077126","tid":810631,"uid":66923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T06:32:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/08/134254_3dd058642183e707acbde558282075f8.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F08%2F134254_3dd058642183e707acbde558282075f8.JPG&h=0bd118d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.androidsloth.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/SurvivalHeroesF.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.androidsloth.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F07%2FSurvivalHeroesF.webp&h=81869633&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n官方網站 : <a href=\"http://survivalheroes.snail.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsurvivalheroes.snail.com%2F&d=PCUYpi8GHLPn0qR1q7n%2Fxy7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=c69dfe0e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://survivalheroes.snail.com/</a><br />\nFacebook: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/survivalheroes\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsurvivalheroes&d=PCUYpi8GHLPn0qR1q7n%2Fxy7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=92cbc562\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/survivalheroes</a><br />\nTwitter: <a href=\"https://twitter.com/Survival_Heroes\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSurvival_Heroes&d=PCUYpi8GHLPn0qR1q7n%2Fxy7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=45b5629b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/Survival_Heroes</a><br />\nInstagram: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/survival_heroes\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fsurvival_heroes&d=PCUYpi8GHLPn0qR1q7n%2Fxy7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=16f21109\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/survival_heroes</a><br />\nYouTube: <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/c/SurvivalHeroes\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fc%2FSurvivalHeroes&d=PCUYpi8GHLPn0qR1q7n%2Fxy7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=a6d0612a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/c/SurvivalHeroes</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6E3P0vyiZkw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D6E3P0vyiZkw&d=PCUYpi8GHLPn0qR1q7n%2Fxy7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=af1d9d9f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6E3P0vyiZkw</a><br />\n<br />\n遊戲簡介<br />\nSurvival Heroes是一款多人競技生存遊戲 MOBA + Battle Royale，把生存競技和魔幻風格完美結合，採用了獨特的戰鬥引擎，你將要去和你的敵人展開刺激的戰鬥，遊戲中的玩法有趣，操作簡單，擁有幾十種武器供你收集，體驗探索和征服的樂趣，和魔幻生物廝殺，並探索魯特大地，收集各種各樣的武器和裝備，讓你存活機率變得更大。<br />\n<br />\nMOBA + Battle Royale<br />\n傳統的MOBA遊戲操作使其上手十分簡單！每位玩家在每場遊戲開始時都享有同等的待遇。拿上拾到的初始武器與玩家展開公平對決，探索大量危險生物和戰利品！還要小心草叢和迷霧，因為你永遠不會知道那裏有什麽。<br />\n<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/ijHzTDj_xIqlFtOrg4fekABcHKpkjm3sDP_Rgwlc6Sd-aDc4JzQq843CxAFMA7r2Fc8=w2458-h1150-rw\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flh3.googleusercontent.com%2FijHzTDj_xIqlFtOrg4fekABcHKpkjm3sDP_Rgwlc6Sd-aDc4JzQq843CxAFMA7r2Fc8%3Dw2458-h1150-rw&h=de4e9bf7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/SAF0iU38MpcOPVbk5w1IrYlT4VC1LYI3IuBEoVOdD5MiFf-72Mj34NB89-GF6CmoBo9M=w2458-h1150-rw\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flh3.googleusercontent.com%2FSAF0iU38MpcOPVbk5w1IrYlT4VC1LYI3IuBEoVOdD5MiFf-72Mj34NB89-GF6CmoBo9M%3Dw2458-h1150-rw&h=70c67fb2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n遊戲玩法<br />\n遊戲講述了一群冒險者機緣巧合觸發了時空裂痕，降臨在一片充滿魔法的大陸上。然而這片大陸充滿了恐怖的魔法屏障，冒險者們為了生存，食物，資源而進行廝殺怪物的一場求生之旅，最後只有一隊人才能逃出這片大陸，成為最後的倖存者。超大的場景地圖，千奇百怪的生物，等待玩家去探險和征服，角色所有裝備都需靠拾取而獲得，更有各種強力技能。遊戲採用暗黑美式卡通風，造型特別，真實感強烈，特效技能華麗。<br />\n<br />\n遊戲特色<br />\n龐大的魔幻地圖和對戰世界<br />\n百種多變的技能和英雄<br />\n全新大逃殺模式，緊張刺激<br />\n不斷縮小的安全區和隨機刷新裝備<br />\n<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/GR6Yq39pt5hPQv4rhRIpDe_f3auQ-nOZ-__bAytXKhNEg4XZ7jogrAi7WQMAOGnwjy4=w2458-h1150-rw\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flh3.googleusercontent.com%2FGR6Yq39pt5hPQv4rhRIpDe_f3auQ-nOZ-__bAytXKhNEg4XZ7jogrAi7WQMAOGnwjy4%3Dw2458-h1150-rw&h=ab1e5480&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/c426noWe1cefJ2O7E2l-aLhMOK531gP1VPmT7-kL2-d8ZTNfjAGVHY1U-d00ooNiRAGK=w2458-h1150-rw\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flh3.googleusercontent.com%2Fc426noWe1cefJ2O7E2l-aLhMOK531gP1VPmT7-kL2-d8ZTNfjAGVHY1U-d00ooNiRAGK%3Dw2458-h1150-rw&h=82dded02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n各種武器和物品<br />\n生存英雄包含近30種不同的武器，可以為英雄提供數百種獨特的選擇。你可以使用激烈的火力以你的方式殺死所有人，或者如果你喜歡鬼鬼祟祟的方式，你可以設置陷阱，潛伏並等待敵人。<br />\n<br />\n撿起屬於你的裝備<br />\n無需再靠購買裝備來獲勝。在Survival Heroes中，考驗的是你的技術與運氣。要成為真正的生還者，你需要在最佳時刻挑出最佳裝備。<br />\n<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/iB5kIclgmdD3zT9lDY9acggUX7_8JoJvhaABQXQZAyVfCmMjgaXtsE--PbmeJX76to3o=w2458-h1150-rw\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flh3.googleusercontent.com%2FiB5kIclgmdD3zT9lDY9acggUX7_8JoJvhaABQXQZAyVfCmMjgaXtsE--PbmeJX76to3o%3Dw2458-h1150-rw&h=6bfde3ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【遊戲畫面】<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UfiIAFTa1c0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DUfiIAFTa1c0&d=PCUYpi8GHLPn0qR1q7n%2Fxy7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=d9729b1d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UfiIAFTa1c0</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=y-sOLG5Onk8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dy-sOLG5Onk8&d=PCUYpi8GHLPn0qR1q7n%2Fxy7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=5ac18187\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=y-sOLG5Onk8</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://survivalheroes.snail.com/upload/2018/0830/a7